Oh, this live brings back memories.
Good work!

Oh, Amana, could you
come over here for a moment?

?
Sure!

Wow!
It's a photo from when you first joined the office!

Ah, nostalgic, right?
It's from our first live.

Hmm, but...
looking at it now...

It doesn't seem like I've changed much,
Amana, wonder if she's growing up...

Huh? It's totally different!
Your expression, your posture...

Maybe, but I feel like there's more sparkle in this one...
Am I imagining things?

Perhaps that's a sign that Amana has become more
discerning. Don't worry, you're even more charming now.
That makes me feel a bit embarrassed...
Oh, by the way, Producer-san...

- Amana is at her own pace,
I'm going to change a little bit at a time.

For that reason, I'm going to enjoy the
unit live with all my might first!

Yeah, I'm looking forward to it... but... sometimes,
the moments of change happen in an instant, right?

Y-Yeah, maybe...
but... yeah... I feel like that too...

Producer-san!
Don't miss that instant!
